DESCRIPTION:

This is an open beta of COD4 Profiler V1.0  by CLEANZ.


FEATURES:

    * Compatible with:    Vista XP,   UAC/Virtual Folder,   Hidden Files,   x64 x32
    
    * Back-up:            Save  &#039;Player Profiles&#039;  and  &#039;Server Favourites&#039;  in a 
      time stamped folder  

    * Restore:            Includes a shortcut back to game directory with each 
      saved profile for easy profile restore.
   
    * Search and detect:  Find ALL cod4 profiles stored on ALL partitions(C-Z)/HD&#039;s
    
    * Remembers:          Profile locations from previous searches(if saved).

    * Sound               Let me know if this is annoying?
 

INSTALLATION:

    * Put  PROFILER-v1.1_CLEANZ.exe  in a safe location, this will also be used to
      store your saved profiles, ie a different HD or partition. 
   
    * Unpack/Right-Click    PROFILER-v1.1_CLEANZ.exe 
   
    * Open  \PROFILER-v1.1_CLEANZ  and right-click  PROFILER-v1.1_CLEANZ.EXE to 
      create shortcut for your desktop
    
    * Start  PROFILER-v1.1_CLEANZ.EXE  from desktop shortcut
